  "The function equals 1 at x = 1": "",
  "The function has exactly one zero": "",
  "The function has a slope of 1": "",
  "A one-to-one (injective) function maps distinct inputs to distinct outputs: if f(a) = f(b) then a = b. Graphically, it passes the horizontal line test, and only one-to-one functions have inverses.": "",
  "What is 'mathematical induction' used for?": "",
