  "Graphing polynomial functions": "",
  "Finding the nth term of a sequence": "",
  "Proving a statement is true for all positive integers by proving a base case and an inductive step": "",
  "Mathematical induction proves statements for all positive integers by: (1) proving it for n = 1 (base case), and (2) showing that if it holds for n = k, it also holds for n = k+1 (inductive step).": "",
  "What does 'composition of functions' mean?": "",
